            "text": "<p>Let me introduce myself; my name is Nirmal, and when I was a kid, mangoes were not just a fruit but a gateway to a world of stories and cherished memories. The sweet and luscious taste of mangoes always reminds me of carefree days, filled with laughter and adventure.</p><p></p>",
