        "text_Lr834m": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Driven by nostalgia and a desire to share love and taste with the rest of the world, I set out on a journey to create Mangobite. In 2016, the idea was just a fantasy, but its ultimate goal was to become a hub for fresh produce and services from all over the world. I’ll never forget that first Sunday, when my family and I set up a cute mango stall at the Avondale Farmers Market. Although we did not have high hopes, the overwhelming demand from customers ultimately reinforced our faith. Thus, Mangobite was born.</p>"
